### Create transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Create deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-22222",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create withdrawal
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-22222",
  "amount": 40.25,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### List all transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions

### Get transactions for account
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Get transfer transactions in date range
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?type=transfer&from=2024-01-01&to=2099-12-31

### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get account summary
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### Invalid transaction example
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "BAD",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": -10,
  "currency": "DOGE",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Invalid deposit with forbidden fromAccount
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-22222",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid withdrawal with forbidden toAccount
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-22222",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}
